# Ringmaster is cross-platform and its hooks launch through a POSIX `sh` shim,
# so every text file is normalized to LF in the repo — identical behavior on
# macOS, Linux, WSL, and Windows (Git-Bash). Prevents CRLF from sneaking into
# the shell launcher or Python hooks on Windows checkouts.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
LICENSE text eol=lf
